		<div id="comment_body_64752374"><p>The point is, though, that you are creating a sentient being without its consent and with no way of knowing if it will judge it's life as a net positive or negative.</p><p>You're making kids because YOU want them, not because they want to exist and need your help.</p></div>
	</div>

